products.product_title: Puma X La France Men Shoes
products.product_description: Give your everyday look a LaMelo Ball-style twist with the PUMA LaFrance Low. A perfect collision of Melo’s “Not From Here” fashion sense and PUMA’s sporty design, these silhouettes look as electrifying as the point guard’s style of play. Inspired by the chunky, skater-like aesthetics, these sneakers are designed to leave a long-lasting impression—thanks to Melo-specific callouts on the midsole and outsole, and his personal La Francé brand. Lace up and “Become Melo” off the court with the PUMA LaFrance Low. PUMA LaFrance Low features: Eye-catching upper lapped over the vamp elevates the look. Fat laces offer a snug fit and provide a stable feel. External heel counter ensures a secure fit. Full-length EVA internal midsole provides superior cushioning and support. Plush, thick foam brings all-day comfort. Fully wrapped-around rubber cupsole enhances stability. Melo-specific decals as raised bubbles add a pop of style. Textured outsole surface with La France and PUMA callouts delivers a striking finish.
